    <!-- Do not touch the description here in the nuspec file. Description is imported during update from the Readme.md file -->
    <description>
      Zotero is free and open-source reference management software to manage bibliographic data and 
      related research materials (such as PDF files). Notable features include web browser integration, 
      online syncing, generation of in-text citations, footnotes and bibliographies, 
      as well as integration with the word processors 
      Microsoft Word, LibreOffice, OpenOffice.org Writer and NeoOffice.
    </description>
